# Supabase rules

**51 migrations** through `050_profiles_age_training.sql` plus `045a`. Apply in strict order. `supabase db push` or paste into SQL Editor ‚Äî both work.

## Tables (12)

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `profiles` | One row per auth user. `plan`, Stripe IDs, `stack_photo_r2_key`, demographics (`biological_sex`, `date_of_birth`, `training_experience`). |
| `user_stacks` | One row per `(user_id, profile_id)`. `stack` JSONB holds compounds. `public_share_id`, `share_feed_visible`. |
| `user_vials` | `peptide_id`, `concentration_mcg_ml`, `bac_water_ml`, `vial_size_mg`, `reconstituted_at`, `expires_at`, `desired_dose_mcg`, `photo_r2_key`, `status`. |
| `dose_logs` | `peptide_id`, `vial_id` (null for oral/nasal/topical), `dose_mcg` OR `dose_count`+`dose_unit`, `dosed_at`, `session_label`, `route_kind`. |
| `member_profiles` | Sub-profiles per user. `display_name`, `handle`, `display_handle`, `avatar_url`, `bio`, `goals`, `language`, `wake_time`, `schedule_shift`, `demo_sessions_shown`, `current_streak`, `consecutive_days`, `is_default`, `social_*_handle`, `locale_*`. |
| `body_metrics` | Scoped per profile. Weight/height/BF%, InBody/DEXA fields. |
| `member_follows` | `(follower_id, following_id)`, unique constraint. |
| `network_feed` | `stack_id` for stack shares, `dose_log_id` for dose posts. `public_visible` flag, `expires_at` TTL. |
| `notifications` | `user_id`, `actor_id`, `type`, `read_at`, `nav_target`. |
| `member_fasts` | `fast_type`, `started_at`, `target_hours`, `ended_at`. |
| `shopping_lists` | Saved shopping list snapshots. |
| `query_log` | AI query analytics. **Not** for rate limiting ‚Äî that's KV. |

**Removed in migration 047:** `ai_queries`. Do not reference it.

## RPCs (15)

| RPC | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `update_user_plan(uuid, text)` | **The only way to change `profiles.plan`.** Sets `app.allow_plan_change` session flag. Revoked from PUBLIC, granted to `service_role`. |
| `get_daily_ai_count(uuid)` | Legacy; KV is primary rate limit now. |
| `get_network_feed()` | Feed joined with `member_profiles` + `user_stacks` for caller. Filtered by ownership + follow graph. |
| `get_public_network_dose_feed()` | Public dose feed (no auth). Filters by `public_visible = true AND expires_at > now()`. |
| `get_shared_stack(text)` | Public read of stack by share id. |
| `get_follow_counts(uuid)` | Follower + following counts. |
| `get_user_profile_stats(uuid)` | Aggregated stats for a member profile. |
| `recalculate_member_profile_streak(uuid)` | Called by dose_logs trigger. |
| `increment_member_profile_demo_sessions(uuid)` | Called when user enters main app. |
| `member_profile_public_by_handle_lookup(text)` | Case-insensitive handle resolver. |
| `handle_new_user()` | Trigger fn: seeds `profiles` + empty `user_stacks` on signup. |
| `set_updated_at()` | Generic updated_at trigger fn. |
| `notify_new_follower_from_follow()` | Inserts notification on new follow. |
| `dose_logs_touch_member_streak()` | Calls streak recalculation. |
| `profiles_enforce_plan_change()` | Rejects plan updates without session flag. |

## Triggers

- `on_auth_user_created` on `auth.users` ‚Üí creates `profiles` + empty `user_stacks`
- `profiles_enforce_plan_change` on `profiles` BEFORE UPDATE ‚Üí rejects plan changes unless `app.allow_plan_change = 'true'`
- `*_updated_at` on 8 tables ‚Üí BEFORE UPDATE, calls `set_updated_at()`
- `dose_logs_recalc_member_streak` on `dose_logs` AFTER INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE ‚Üí `recalculate_member_profile_streak`
- `member_follows_notify_followee` on `member_follows` AFTER INSERT ‚Üí inserts `notifications`

## RLS model

Every table has RLS enabled. Policies are `auth.uid() = user_id` style, except:

- `member_profiles: select own` ‚Äî scoped via user_id match (not profile_id)
- `network_feed: select public active` ‚Äî public filtered by `public_visible = true AND expires_at > now()`
- `user_stacks: select network feed` ‚Äî lets followers see feed-visible stacks
- `member_follows: select authenticated` ‚Äî anyone signed in can read (for counters)

**Read `docs/security/rls-audit.md` before touching policies.**

## Schema invariants

- `profiles.plan` ‚àà `('entry', 'pro', 'elite', 'goat')` ‚Äî CHECK in 001
- `member_profiles.handle` lowercase, 3‚Äì32 chars, regex `^[a-zA-Z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9_.-]{1,30}[a-zA-Z0-9]$`, no `..`, `member_profiles_handle_format_chk`
- `member_profiles.bio` ‚â§ 500 chars (migration 031)
- `member_fasts.target_hours` > 0, ‚â§ 2160 (90 days, client-enforced)
- `user_stacks` unique on `(user_id, profile_id)` ‚Äî one stack per profile slot
- One default `member_profile` per user (`is_default = true`)

